#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: makeiteasy-popup.php
msgid "MakeITeasy Popup"
msgstr "MakeITeasy Popup"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:68
msgid "Welcome to Make IT easy popup!"
msgstr ""

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:74
msgid "To insert popup into the post, find 'MakeITeasy Popup' block under Widgets group."
msgstr "Kako biste umetnuli skočni prozor u post, pronađite blok 'MakeITeasy Popup' u grupi Widgeti."

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:90
msgid "Content"
msgstr "Sadržaj"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:94
msgid "Inside popup block, you can insert any number of blocks, like you would normally with group, column, quote block etc."
msgstr "Unutar bloka skočnog prozora, možete umetnuti bilo koji broj blokova, kao što biste to normalno radili s grupom, stupcem, blokom citata itd."

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:111
msgid "Opening conditions"
msgstr "Uvjeti otvaranja"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:118
msgid "Probably most important setting is opening condition."
msgstr "Vjerojatno najvažnija postavka je uvjet otvaranja."

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:126
msgid "Popup can be opened after some time passes, on scroll, on click, on hover, or on exit intent. All these conditions can be combined with opening referer."
msgstr "Pop-up se može otvoriti nakon nekog vremena, na scroll, na klik, na hover ili na namjeru izlaska. Svi ovi uvjeti mogu se kombinirati s uvjetom referera."

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:144
msgid "Selectors"
msgstr "Selektori"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:148
msgid "Some opening conditions, such as 'on click,' require an element to trigger the popup when interacted with."
msgstr "Neki uvjeti otvaranja, poput 'na klik', zahtijevaju element koji će pokrenuti skočni prozor kada se s njim interagira."

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:156
msgid "To achieve this, you need to provide the CSS selector of the element that will trigger the popup, whether it's clicked, scrolled to, or hovered over."
msgstr "Kako biste to postigli, trebate pružiti CSS selektor elementa koji će pokrenuti skočni prozor, bilo da se klikne, skrola do njega ili se pređe mišem preko njega."

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:174
msgid "What is referer?"
msgstr "Što je referer?"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:178
msgid "Referer is simply the URL of the page where user was before coming to current page."
msgstr "Referer je jednostavno URL stranice na kojoj je korisnik bio prije dolaska na trenutnu stranicu."

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:184
msgid "MDN documentation:"
msgstr "MDN dokumentacija:"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:190
msgctxt "external link text"
msgid "Referer"
msgstr "Referer"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:211
msgid "Referer condition"
msgstr "Referer uvjet"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:218
msgid "If referer field is left unfilled, there will be no condition for referer. Otherwise, popup will open only if any part of referer matches the string in this field."
msgstr "Ako polje referera ostane nepopunjeno, neće postojati uvjet za referer. U suprotnom, skočni prozor će se otvoriti samo ako bilo koji dio referera odgovara nizu u ovom polju."

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:223
msgid "This condition is combined with opening condition, so popup will open only if both conditions are met."
msgstr "Ovaj uvjet se kombinira s uvjetom otvaranja, tako da će se skočni prozor otvoriti samo ako su oba uvjeta zadovoljena."

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:244
msgid "You have possibility to set when dismissed popup will appear again. The timer's state is preserved across user sessions, ensuring a consistent reappearance interval."
msgstr "Imate mogućnost postaviti kada će se odbijeni skočni prozor ponovno pojaviti. Stanje tajmera se čuva između korisničkih sesija, osiguravajući dosljedan interval ponovnog pojavljivanja."

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:261
msgid "Close button"
msgstr "Gumb za zatvaranje"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:265
msgid "Changing the close button is so far possible only programmatically by using filters. It is planned to add UI in the settings for uploading custom image."
msgstr "Promjena gumba za zatvaranje do sada je moguća samo programatski korištenjem filtera. Planirano je dodati korisničko sučelje u postavkama za učitavanje prilagođene slike."

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:271
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:311
msgid "Read in the"
msgstr "Pročitaj u"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:273
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:313
msgctxt "external link text"
msgid "plugin readme"
msgstr "readme dodatka"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:279
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:319
msgid "how to change the close button."
msgstr "kako promijeniti gumb za zatvaranje."

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:284
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:324
msgid "You can also refer to readme for other questions you might have"
msgstr "Također se možete obratiti readme-u za druga pitanja koja biste mogli imati"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/nux/tips.jsx:302
msgid "Show again after x days"
msgstr "Prikaži ponovno nakon x dana"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/components/BlockSidebar.jsx:150
msgid "On exit intent"
msgstr "Na izlaznu namjeru"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/components/BlockSidebar.jsx:266
msgid "Activate after (seconds)"
msgstr "Aktiviraj nakon (sekundi)"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/components/BlockSidebar.jsx:270
msgid "Set to 0 to activate immediately."
msgstr "Postavite na 0 za odmah aktiviranje."

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/components/BlockSidebar.jsx:295
msgid "Only on referer URL match (optional)"
msgstr "Samo ako se URL referera podudara (opcionalno)"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/components/BlockSidebar.jsx:303
msgid "URL part"
msgstr "Dio URL-a"

#: build/index.js:1
#: src/components/BlockSidebar.jsx:573
msgid "For a fixed width or to correct block display issues inside the popup, set the width here."
msgstr "Za fiksnu širinu ili za ispravljanje problema s prikazom bloka unutar skočnog prozora, postavite širinu ovdje."

